cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper involves the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) to analyze kinematic data from surgical procedures. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) as it aims to provide personalized feedback to trainees.
